Deg usamar n Bgayet, ideg ɛerḍen wid iḥeḍren ad walin liḥala n yigḍaḍ-a n waman.
Ad ten-siḍnen deg wacḥal i d-yeqqimen.
Ulama yewɛer akken ad tafeḍ leḥsab, ssawaḍen yirgazen n uḥraz n tẓegwa ad sɛun tikti.
Ad sennden ɣef ufmiḍi i d-ufan.
Kkin deg warmud-a n usiḍen i d-yellan lqaɛ n wasif Ageryun.
Tigawin-a n usefqed d usiḍen n yigḍaḍ yettɛeccicen, llant-d i lmend n wass amaḍalan n yigḍaḍ imhujar.
Wid yekkin s wudem unsib deg uqeddic.
Llan wid yettruḥun akken kan ad walin, neɣ ad ɛiwnen ma zemren.
Send ad kecmeɣ ɣer uɣerbaz, lliɣ selleɣ i uẓawan n waṭas n yicennayen, gar-asen.
Meɛtub Lwennas, Ayt Mengellat, Sliman Σazem d wiyaḍ.
Ufiɣ-d tafransist d tifrat i wakken ad d-iniɣ ayen ttwaliɣ d wayen txemmimeɣ.
Ayen ssaramaɣ, d wayen i yi-iceɣben.
Mass Mebruk Sennun, Farid Idrisi akked tnaẓurt Bahiya Ḥamdi i yi-d-ixedmen unuɣ i wammud-iw n yisefra.
Ma yella nuɣal-d ɣef wamek tettwasen tuddsa, ad naf d akken d iẓeḍwa inmettiyen.
 Allal n usiweḍ i icudden gar leqdicat n tuddsa akked umsider.
Nxeddem aseɛlem deg merra taɣulin.
Ayen yeɛnan isafaren n wučči.
 Wid teɛna temsalt n waya ad d-fkeɣ imedyaten yelhan ɣef wanect-agi.
Asentel-agi, yegla-d s waṭas n lexsarat deg terwiḥin di tmurt-nneɣ.
D ayen i d aɣ-yeǧǧan, nxeddem anect-agi.
 Ad nesseḥbiber xerṣum cwit.
Neɛreḍ ad ten-nwelleh.
Ad rren ddehn-nsen ɣer wayen yeɛnan tifesniwin n usismeḍ n yisufar-agi.
Ladɣa deg wussan n uzɣal.
Am wakken daɣen, yella wayen ur ilaq ara ad yini.
Llant kra n tɣawsiwin ur ilaq ara ad nemmeslay fell-asent.
Isalaɣen mačči kan d wagi ara yilin.
Ilaq iɛeggalen ad issinen amek ara qablen annar.
Sya d afella, ad d-nheggi yiwen.
Imi aman-agi akked yiẓmi-agi, ad ruḥen seg umkan ɣer wayeḍ akken ddaw n yiṭij.
Amsider ara yeswen isafaren-agi ur nettwaḥrez ara deg tasmuḍi.
Ur ten-xeddmen ara deg yimukan i ilaqen akken ur xettren ara.
Ffkan-d yiwen n wumuɣ n kra n yisufar akked leswam-nsen.
Aɣbel a-t-an ulac wid ara iɛassen imestjaren-agi.
Seg wakken myeḥmalen aṭas, uγalen am sin n yiḍudan n ufus.
Ula d lwaεda mi asen-d-tettunefk, wa ittbuddu wayeḍ s uḥric yelhan.
Ismektiyen n Tefsut n tmanyin d Tefsut taberkant i d-yellan deg wussan iɛeddan.
Yettuɣal-d yal mi ara d-yeḥḍer waggur n yebrir.
Yella-d usmekti-ines deg kra n tamiwin n Bgayet am Cmini.
Isaragen d tejmilin i yuɣalen ladɣa i wid yettwaṭṭfen ɣer leḥbus lawan-nni.
Tella-d tuffɣa n ugdud aqbayli ɣer yiberdan deg temnaḍt n Ssumam.
Tuffɣa meqqren mbeɛd tin n Tefsut n yimaziɣen.
Ffɣen-d yisnawiyen, iselmaden, ixeddamen d wid ur nxeddem ara.
Tettwasuddes akken ilaq, d ayen i tt-yeǧǧan ad tekcem deg umezruy.
D ayen i d-yeglan s tyitiwin d uḥbas n waṭas n yimeɣnasen.
Ḥekmen gar setta n wagguren ar xemsa n yiseggasen.
Tikwal llant tuddar s sin n leǧwamaɛ, di lawan ideg timesgidiwin ttenqasent rennunt.
Ama s ufus n umdan neɣ n zzman.
Aredmani, ayen i d-yeḍḥan d ttbut akka tura, d annerni i ttnernin leǧwamaɛ.
Rnu ɣer-s, deg waṭas n temnaḍin, mačči d lḥukuma i yettxellisen lebni n leǧwamaɛ.
 Di taddart n Ayt Tɛisiwt yella yekker umennuɣ gar snat n tamiwin.
Tekker terbaɛt i lebni n wis sin, amzun mačči d yiwen n ubrid i ḍefren.
Daɣen, ussan-a kan i yeldi yiwen n lǧamaɛ d amaynut.
Akken yebɣu yili, yewwi-d ad d-tres i uskasi taluft n lebni n leǧwamaɛ.
Yir tasnakta tɣemmi, rnu-as imezdaɣ i yettnernin di tuddar.
Ma yerra yiwen iman-is d wakal-is d leǧwamaɛ, ulac amḍiq ara d-yaf xir i usemres n teflest-is.
Ma yella d inelmaden n yiswiren ineggura, mazal ttṛaǧun-ten-id yikayaden.
 Inelmaden-a dɣa, fkan-as ddḥis ussan-a i tɣuri d uheggi i ukayad-a.
D ayen i izemmren ad ten-iḍuṛ.
I wakken anelmad ur ihellek ara iman-is s ttexmam, d tɣuri ur d-nettawi agemmuḍ.
Ayagi, i wakken ad asen-fken afus n tallelt i yinelmaden n uswir wis semmus.
Iselmaden ara sen-yernun timsirin, d wid yesεan tarmit deg useɣṛi.
Ssnen amek i d-ttasen yisteqsiyen.
Ṭebbaq, ṭebbaq, lexrif yewwa, nekni nqebba.
Gummaɣ ad afeɣ tifyar-iw deg common voice.
Stufaɣ-asen-d i warazen.
D aḍummu i ṭṭummuɣ arazen a nnger-nwen.
